      "author": "doge-liang",
      "description": "Plugin-review fix release.\n\n- **Fixed \\`obsidianmd/no-unsupported-api\\` Error** — \\`Vault.createFolder()\\` (used by the new \"New diagram location\" feature in 0.2.0) requires Obsidian 1.4.0+, newer than this plugin's declared \\`minAppVersion\\` (1.0.0). It's now guarded with \\`requireApiVersion('1.4.0')\\`, falling back to the always-available \\`DataAdapter.mkdir\\` on older Obsidian builds — no functional change on any currently-supported Obsidian version.",
