      "author": "doge-liang",
      "description": "Feature release — implements the requests from #1. Thanks @GandalfUFR!\n\n- **New diagram location** setting: create new diagrams in the vault root (default), the same folder as the current note, or a fixed folder of your choice (created automatically if missing).\n- **New entry points**: a ribbon button, and a **\"New drawio diagram\"** item in the file explorer's folder context menu (creates the diagram in that folder).\n- **Preview alignment** setting: keep previews centered (default) or left-align them — applies to both `![[file.drawio]]` embeds and ```drawio code blocks.",
