      "description": "Review-round fixes.\n\n- Don't detach the plugin's leaves in onunload (keeps the view's user-chosen location).\n- Address Obsidian lint warnings (popout-window-safe globals, no unsafe any, etc.).\n- Keep the settings tab on the supported display() API (compatible with the declared minAppVersion).\n- Default to the bundled offline editor, with automatic fallback to the online diagrams.net editor when the webapp isn't installed.\n\nInstall: copy `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/drawio-editor/`. For the fully offline editor, see the README.",
