      "description": "First release.\n\nEmbed, preview, and edit draw.io (diagrams.net) diagrams directly in your notes.\n\n- Code blocks (```drawio), standalone `.drawio` files (inline editor in the tab), and `![[file.drawio]]` embeds — rendered in both editing and reading views.\n- Online editor by default (loaded from diagrams.net); switch to a bundled offline editor or a custom embed URL in settings.\n- Diagrams stored as readable, uncompressed multi-line XML.\n- Desktop only.\n\nInstall: copy `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/drawio/`. For the offline editor, see the README.",
